com.metreeca.rest.handlers.actors

Class Browser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.Delegator
      • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.Actor<Browser>
        • com.metreeca.rest.handlers.actors.Browser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Handler

    public final class Browser
extends Actor<Browser>
    Basic container browser.

    Handles retrieval requests on linked data basic container.

    Response shape-driven RDFFormat body
    If the request includes shape, the response includes the RDF description of the request focus item, containing the RDF descriptions of the virtual container items matched by the redacted linked data shape.
    If the request contains a Prefer header requesting the LDP.PREFER_EMPTY_CONTAINER representation, virtual item descriptions are omitted.
    If the request contains a filtering query, only matching virtual container item descriptionss are included.
    Response shapeless RDFFormat body
    Warning / Shapeless container retrieval is not yet supported and is reported with a Response.NotImplemented HTTP status code.

    If the request includes a shape, the response includes the derived shape actually used in the container retrieval process, redacted according to request user roles, Form.relate task, Form.verify mode and Form.digest view.

    Regardless of the operating mode, RDF data is retrieved from the system graph database.

    See Also:
